Detailed Description

Definitions for the message queue system used for telegrams and communucation like debugging (also rs232 communication).

enum emsg_state

Status of the message.

Enumerator:
MSG_FREE

MSG_ALLOC

MSG_SENDING

MSG_WAIT_ACK
